research_municipality_step.notes: The elected officials for Bertram City, TX, include the Mayor and five Council Members. Mike Dickinson was elected Mayor in May 2021, with his current term running from May 2024 to May 2026. John Baladez serves as Mayor Pro-tem and Council Member, with a term from May 2021 to May 2027. Other Council Members are Anthony DeFrancisis (term May 2025-May 2027), Lane Shipp (term May 2025-May 2026), Randal Fisher (term May 2024-May 2026), and James Predmore (term May 2024-May 2026). All council positions appear to be at-large, as no specific wards or districts are mentioned.
